Function fn_Delete_Column(in_rng_Base_Range_For_New_Column As Range)

'-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
'         Created By: Tarun Chauhan
'         Date: 22-May-2022

' This function Deletes the Worksheet from the given Workbook Object

'What do you need to provide to the function
  'It needs the base range address of the Column to be deleted - Example: ActiveSheet.Range("A1")
'-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

in_rng_Base_Range_For_New_Column.EntireColumn.Delete xlShiftToLeft

End Function
